org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan

Class CompleteRowKeyAssembler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan.CompleteRowKeyAssembler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompleteRowKey, RowKeyScanAssembler

    public class CompleteRowKeyAssembler
extends java.lang.Object
implements RowKeyScanAssembler, CompleteRowKey
    Assembles a row key where each field within the composite row key is constructed based a set of given query predicates.
    Since:
    0.5.5
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    DataGraphConfig, TableConfig, UserDefinedField, PredefinedField, PreDefinedFieldName
